          <div class="grid_17 omega articleTitle">About the SROI Online Training<hr /></div>
          <div class="grid_17 omega text_content">
            <p>This online training has been developed by Shubha Kumar, MPH, PhD(c), based upon a combination of academic research and experience with SROI Analysis (including completion of the SROI training for accredited practitioners offered by the SROI Network).  This online training was developed to increase awareness and potential use of SROI Analysis through easily accessible web instruction- the first of its kind.  Furthermore, it was designed to showcase how organizations from diverse sectors, such as the international health and development sector, may apply and derive value from SROI Analysis. </p>
            <p>While there are excellent reading materials and in-person trainings on how to do an SROI Analysis (see the <a href="http://www.thesroinetwork.org" target="blank">SROI Network Website</a>), this online training was designed to supplement such learning opportunities and to provide a forum for those interested in learning how to apply SROI Analysis within their organizations but prefer the flexibility and convenience of online training (including video and audio instruction) which can be accessed at anytime in any part of the world.</p>
            <p>Benefits of this online training on SROI Analysis include:</p>
            <p>
               <ul>
                  <li>Accessible anywhere anytime (24/7) via internet</li>
                  <li>Multiple logins available for each organization</li>
                  <li>Additional support services available in-person, by phone/email as needed</li>
                  <li>No costs of travel/lodging to receive training (all that's needed is an internet connection!)</li>
                  <li>Developed by an individual with both professional and academic expertise</li>
               </ul>
            </p>
            <p>For more information or to request login(s) to the full training or the demo version below, please email Shubha Kumar at <a href="mailto:skumar@globalsroi.com">skumar@globalsroi.com</a></p>

